25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：在学习 Windows 本地提权思路和枚举方法的读者。\n阅读前提：了解 Windows 权限模型、服务、计划任务和用户组。\n核心收获：把 UAC 绕过、令牌窃取、服务劫持和自动化枚举联系起来。\n说明：利用链是否成立强依赖目标版本、补丁和安全策略。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在渗透测试中，初始访问通常只能获取普通用户权限。要进一步控制系统、访问敏感数据或进行横向移动，权限提升（Privilege Escalation）是必经之路。Windows 系统拥有复杂的权限模型，但同时也存在众多可被利用的提权向量。本文将系统讲解 Windows 提权的核心技术，从权限模型基础到 UAC 绕过、令牌操作、服务劫持等高级技术，配合自动化枚举工具的使用方法。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"windows-权限模型基础","children":["Windows 权限模型基础",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#windows-权限模型基础","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"理解 Windows 提权技术之前，需要先掌握 Windows 权限体系的核心概念。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"用户和用户组","children":["用户和用户组",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#用户和用户组","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Windows 通过用户组来管理权限，关键的内置组包括："}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Administrators"}]," — 完全控制权限"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Users"}]," — 标准用户权限"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Backup Operators"}]," — 可备份/恢复文件，可读取任意文件"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Remote Desktop Users"}]," — 允许 RDP 登录"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Remote Management Users"}]," — 允许 WinRM 连接"]}],"\n"]}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"访问令牌access-token","children":["访问令牌（Access Token）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#访问令牌access-token","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Windows 中每个进程都关联一个访问令牌，令牌包含用户的 SID、所属组和特权列表。关键特权包括："}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"特权名称"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"提权潜力"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"利用方法"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"SeImpersonatePrivilege"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"高"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Potato 系列攻击"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"SeAssignPrimaryTokenPrivilege"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"高"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"令牌替换"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"SeBackupPrivilege"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"高"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"读取任意文件/注册表"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"SeRestorePrivilege"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"高"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"写入任意文件"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"SeTakeOwnershipPrivilege"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"高"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"获取文件所有权"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"SeDebugPrivilege"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"高"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"调试任意进程"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"SeLoadDriverPrivilege"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"高"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"加载内核驱动"}]]}]]}]]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"完整性级别integrity-levels","children":["完整性级别（Integrity Levels）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#完整性级别integrity-levels","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Windows Vista 之后引入的强制完整性控制（MIC）将进程分为不同的完整性级别："}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"System"}]," — 系统级别（内核和系统服务）"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"High"}]," — 管理员级别（提升后的管理员进程）"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Medium"}]," — 标准用户级别（普通用户进程）"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"childre